<Imprint xmlns:Imprint="Render://approach.local">
    <Imprint:Pattern name="Issueform" type="HTML">
        <div class="TabsForm Interface">
            <div class="New">
                <div class="TabBar">
                    <div class="tab-button" id="tabBtn1">Requirements<i class="bi bi-arrow-right"></i></div>
                    <div class="tab-button" id="tabBtn2">Survey<i class="bi bi-arrow-right"></i></div>
                    <div class="tab-button" id="tabBtn3">Review<i class="bi bi-arrow-right"></i></div>
                    <div class="tab-button" id="tabBtn4">Work<i class="bi bi-arrow-right"></i></div>
                    <div class="tab-button" id="tabBtn5">Describe<i class="bi bi-arrow-right"></i></div>
                    <div class="tab-button" id="tabBtn6">Adapt<i class="bi bi-arrow-right"></i></div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div id="tabs_stuff">
                <div class="tab tab1 active Interface InterfaceContent  p-3 pb-0" id="Requirements">
                    <h4>1. Decide a Goal</h4>
                    <p>üéØ What's the goal?</p>
                    <form class="p-3 pt-0 Autoform" data-action="Climb">
                        <div class="mb-3"><label class="form-label">Set a Destination</label><input class="form-control" type="text" name="title" id="title" placeholder="Become a billionaire"></div>
                        <div><label class="form-label">Parent Id</label><input class="form-control" type="text" name="parent_id" value="[@ parentId @]" placeholder="Parent ID"></div>
                        [@ Requirements @]
                    </form>
                    <div><button class="btn btn-primary " id="add-input-group">Add New Requirement</button></div>
                </div>
                <div class="tab tab2 Interface InterfaceContent" id="Survey">
                    <form class="p-3 Autoform" data-action="Survey">
                        <h4 class="pb-3 fw-bolder">2. Survey of the Environment</h4>
                        <p>Note the obstacles, check if the obstacles disqualify the goal, and check if the goal is still worth pursuing.</p>
                        <p>Points of Interest for new Destinations</p>
                        <div id="Interests">
                            [@ Interests @]
                        </div>
                        <div><button class="btn btn-primary " id="add-interest-group" type="reset">Add New Interest</button><button class="btn btn-secondary " id="remove-interest-group" type="reset">Remove Last Point</button></div>
                        <p>Points of Concern and Hazards</p>
                        <div>
                            [@ Obstacles @]
                        </div>
                    </form>
                    <div><button class="btn btn-info " id="add-obstacle" type="button">Add New Obstacle</button><button class="btn btn-secondary " id="remove-obstacle" type="button">Remove Last Obstacle</button></div>
                    <div>
                        <p class="fs-5">Found a problem?</p><button class="btn btn-danger" type="button">üíÄ Give Up</button></div>
                </div>
                <div class="tab tab3 p-3 Interface InterfaceContent" id="Budgets">
                    <h4>3. Review Findings</h4>
                    <div>
                        <p class="fs-5"><span>üïßÔ∏è Budget:</span></p>
                        <form class="Autoform" data-action="Time">
                            <div>
                                [@ Budgets @]
                            </div>
                        </form>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="tab tab4 p-3 Interface InterfaceContent">
                    <h4>4. Time To Work</h4>
                    <p><span>üî® Action:</span> Work on the goal</p>
                    <form class="Autoform" data-action="Work">
                        <div class="mb-3"><textarea class="form-control" name="document_progress" rows="3">
                            [@ Progress @]
                        </textarea></div>
                        <div class="form-text">Continue to work on the goal and document your progress here.</div>
                    </form>
                </div>
                <div class="tab tab5 Interface InterfaceContent">
                    <h4>5. Describe your Work</h4>
                    <p><span>üìî Reflection:</span> Describe your work</p>
                    <form class="Autoform" data-action="Describe">
                        <div class="mb-3"><label class="form-label">Budget: Expectations vs Reality</label><select class="form-select" name="budget_res" aria-label="Default select example" aria-describedby="budget-reality">Choose an option<option value="1">Budget Met Expectations</option><option value="2">Budget Exceeded Expectations</option><option value="3">Low Budget</option></select></div>
                        <p>Points of Interest for new Destinations</p>
                        <div id="InterestsD">
                            [@ InterestsD @]
                        </div>
                        <div><button class="btn btn-primary " id="add-interest-d-group" type="button">Add New Interest</button><button class="btn btn-secondary " id="remove-interest-d-group" type="button">Remove Last Point</button></div>
                        <p>Points of Concern and Hazards</p>
                        <div id="Hazards">
                            [@ Hazards @]
                        </div>
                    </form>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="tab tab6">
                <h4>6. Adapt from Finding</h4>
                <p><span>üîß Adapt:</span> Adapt from the findings</p>
                <div class="btn-group btn-group-lg" role="group" aria-label="Basic mixed styles example"><button class="btn btn-warning"><i class="bi bi-arrow-repeat"></i> Iterate</button><button class="btn btn-success"><i class="bi bi-signal"></i> Branch</button></div>
            </div>
            <div>
                <div class="controls">
                    <button type="button" class="visual control btn btn-success mt-3" data-api="/server.php" data-role="autoform" data-api-method="POST" data-intent="{ "REFRESH": { "Climb" : "Update" } }" data-context="{ "_response_target": "#result", "climb_id": "31", "owner": "newtoallofthis123", "repo": "test_for_issues" }">
                        Save
                    </button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </Imprint:Pattern>
</Imprint>

